    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Learning is a lifelong process experienced through connections that are embodied through diverse learning situations. Through cognitive, practical and emotional experiences, transformation occurs through stages, resulting in a continually changing or more experienced person (Jarvis 2009; Illeris 2014).</p>]]></Value>
